{"tid":683795,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[框架倒塌] WTO明年恐停擺！前WTO法官披露原因與美國有關","createTime":"2018-05-30T03:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T15:24:55.000Z","uid":184679,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"02af08a9979d9ba5ba78f35ffe02810e46373bb9","tid":683795,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T03:53:50.000Z","msg":"1位世界貿易組織（WTO）的退休法官近日表示，他認為WTO正在慢慢被勒死，原因是美國不斷地對WTO法官任命行使否決權，並且呼籲所有會員國共同面對這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n根據《路透》報導，1位前世貿組織上訴機構的退休法官拉米雷埃南德斯（Ricardo Ramirez-Hernandez）透露，在去年他從WTO上訴機構退休後，美國一直使用否決權，干預新任法官的任命。<br />\n<br />\nWTO上訴機構正常編制應該要有7個人，但由於美國政權的干預，現在僅有4位法官，其中1位在今年9月任期將屆滿，2位明年將要離職。而無論是何種案件，都需要至少3名法官共同審理，意味著如果美國持續干預任命，WTO的上訴機構明年就會停擺。<br />\n<br />\n美國當局會不斷行使否決權，是為了抗議WTO對美國「不公平」，不過，退休法官拉米雷埃南德斯並沒有單純指責美國的行為，更表示每個WTO的會員國都有責任解決這件事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2441296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2441296&d=5kzrlEfzlIokQJ1uteSlY75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=2924362c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2441296&h=90ecfa85\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2441296</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c476cb614fc7523dc299bed5d7a9bf654531b56b","tid":683795,"uid":100131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:07:13.000Z","msg":"轉個頭中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f81414096f3360454d4bb8f7bf6af928ed808b4","tid":683795,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:11:56.000Z","msg":"因為美帝 trump 想建立新既貿易秩序"},{"pid":"df56ece1e9dd5ce7236769a9fef3e9c23439c82b","tid":683795,"uid":75326,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T05:43:55.000Z","msg":"聯合國順便唔該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <